title: LF high silver - low gold duo
body:
Hi all, 

I am a nocturne mid OTP however can play him top and jungle. 

Looking for a person to duo with to reach Plat by the end of the season and possibly diamond. 

Player must have voice comms 
Player must tilt very rarely and be focused on improving personal play over blaming others. 
Would prefer a jungle/support duo. as that way we can coordinate ganks and roams across the map to secure objectives. 

Add me my IGN is Midturne. 

look forwards to seeing you on the rift!

https://oce.op.gg/summoner/userName=midturne

replies.body:
Hi Midturnem, i'd love to play some trial games with you. Can you also let me know you average win rate on Nocturne?
Regards
Blackestfury
Added . Been Hardstuck Gold 3 for a bit , also a Jungle and Support main.  Looking to tango on the rift with you
Hi there, could you tell me your rank? I'm interested in duoing, but I'd like to know a bit more about your skills.
